-- Changes made 0828: -- RMG / Sportsbetting rollup using .dataai.sub_genre rather than GDS Insights Engine Definition
-- Event-based FTDs via whitelist + deposit-only catchall
-- Minimum of 10 installs per period and $500+ to be included in benchmark
WHEN d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting', 'Fantasy Sports') THEN 'Sportsbetting'
WHERE d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting','Fantasy Sports','Casinos & Gambling')
GROUP BY date, f.os, grouped_category, f.country
PARTITION BY os, grouped_category, country, DATE_TRUNC(date, MONTH)
GROUP BY date, os, grouped_category, total_MAU, country
-- Per (date, geo, os, vertical, format, bundle)
WHEN d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting', 'Fantasy Sports') THEN 'Sportsbetting'
AND d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting','Fantasy Sports','Casinos & Gambling')
-- Event-derived First Deposits (FTD) within D7 using whitelist + first time deposit-only catchall
WHEN d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting', 'Fantasy Sports') THEN 'Sportsbetting'
COALESCE(SUM(f.kpi_actions_d7),0) AS kpi_actions_d7 -- FTDs within D7
AND d.dataai.sub_genre IN ('Sports Betting','Fantasy Sports','Casinos & Gambling')
-- Join performance with FTDs at bundle grain
-- Carry app name + keep bundle for distinct counts
-- Daily rollup by (date, geo, os, vertical)
COUNT(DISTINCT app_market_bundle) AS num_app_bundles -- distinct bundles per day/geo/os/vertical
GROUP BY date, country, os, vertical
ORDER BY m.date, vertical, m.os, m.country;
